title: Independent candidate Arbab Amir wins NA-29 seat
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Arbab Amir Ayub has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-29 Lakki Marwat by securing 68,792 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Saqibullah Khan of Awami National Party (ANP) who bagged 18,888 votes.
Votersâ€™ turn-out remained 39.72 per cent.
